Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:32.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}在彷徨的未來 在狹隘的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:37.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我們探尋光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.74,0:22:41.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}顫抖著的雙手是無力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:44.61,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}吶喊又在消失在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:53.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}然而飛翔的心 不允許一絲的恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:23:01.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}不永恆又何妨 不完美又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:08.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}只要在相互扶持的世界勇敢生存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:15.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}一次次的受傷算什麼 一次次的錯誤算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:21.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}即使是命運 我們也要一起飛越
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:24.94,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}飛向天空的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:31.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}相信著希望的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:32.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}僕たちは彷徨える未来　窮屈な空に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:37.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}光を探している
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.74,0:22:41.20,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}震える手は無力で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:44.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}叫びはまた遠くて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:53.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}だけど飛ぶこころ　恐れではいられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:23:01.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永遠じゃなくでも　完璧じゃなくでも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:08.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}背中合わせの世界を真っ直ぐ生きていく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:15.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}何度傷ついでも　何度間違えでも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:21.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}運命さえ飛び越えて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:24.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}この空の果てまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:31.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}始まりを信じで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.53,0:19:12.23,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Got over it ages ago
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:15.93,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Where we were from the same river
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:19.79,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Thinking about how we lost our minds
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:23.04,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I don't care what's in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:27.20,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}They don't care about old trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.82,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Many wars wherever you go
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:32.66,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Somebody please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.72,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Can we stop all the fights?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.62,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll do it because it's my turn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:41.59,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}But don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:45.73,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}There are people crying everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.78,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's fly away
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:51.74,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}For Earth and Mars today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:53.72,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't stop me now
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:56.58,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Look around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:20:00.12,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}How can we stop the war
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:04.44,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Hello, But Are we sure enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:06.62,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You'll come back tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.72,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}But I need to know that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:11.52,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Look around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:14.92,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So What are we fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.86,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Can I ask you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.29,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Why the sky is blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:20.78,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}There's no difference
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.92,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You and me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:42.34,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't stop me now
